        </mj-text>
        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com/email/images/bucket-wheel-excavators-rare-earth-mining-zhytomyr-ukraine.png" alt="Bucket-wheel excavators mine rare earth materials in the Zhytomyr region of Ukraine" href="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com" />
